Open the file in BINARY MODE using 

vi -b 100-crackme_password

Press ESC key to enter COMMAND MODE

Type the following to SET BINARY 

:set binary

Press ENTER key

Type the following to set NO END OF LINE

:set noel

Press ENTER key

Press i key enter INSERT MODE

Write the following PASSWORD inside the file

abc123

Press ESC key

Type the following to SAVE and EXIT

:wq

Press ENTER key

Git add the file

git add 100-crackme_password

Git commit the file

git commit -m "password for the crackme2"

Git push the file

git push

Check your code to COMFIRM
